오늘 강의
    오늘의 강의: 유튜브 클론코딩: From #3.0 to #3.4
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Code Challenge
    Using the blueprint(https://codesandbox.io/s/a02blueprint-yn6p5?file=/src/server.js) complete the server.js file and create an Express server.
    This server should have 4 GET routes.
    The routes are /, /about, /contact and /login.
    All the routes should return HTML to the client.
